@startuml

title User Profile Overview and Posts Management Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant "Frontend (Website)" as FE
participant "Apache\n(HTTP Server)" as Apache

box "Laravel Application" #LightGreen
  participant "Middleware" as MW
  participant "ProfileController" as PC
  participant "PostController" as PostC
  participant "Eloquent ORM" as ORM
end box

database "MariaDB Database" as DB

note right of User
It is assumed the User is
authenticated/authorized unless an exception occurs.
end note


== Open My Profile Page ==

User -> FE: Open "Mi Perfil"
activate User
activate FE
activate Apache
activate MW
activate PC
activate PostC
activate ORM
activate DB

FE -> Apache: GET /my_profile

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP profile request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display "My profile route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> PC: Pass authenticated and authorized profile request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden
    FE --> User: Display validation or authorization error
end

PC -> ORM: Load authenticated user
ORM -> DB: SELECT current authenticated user record

PC -> ORM: Lending::with(items.equipment)->where(user_id = user.id)
ORM -> DB: SELECT user lending requests with related equipment

PC -> ORM: Post::where(user_id = user.id)->latest()->get()
ORM -> DB: SELECT user posts ORDER BY created_at DESC

PC -> ORM: Review::where(seller_id = user.id)->avg('rating')
ORM -> DB: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

PC -> ORM: Review::where(seller_id = user.id)->count()
ORM -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

alt Profile query success
    DB --> ORM: User profile data, requests, posts, and seller rating stats
    ORM --> PC: Profile datasets retrieved
    PC --> FE: Return my_profile view
    FE --> User: Display profile summary, posts tab, and requests tab
else Profile query failure
    DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> PC: Profile data retrieval failed
    PC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> User: Display system error while loading profile
end


== Filter My Posts ==

User -> FE: Search posts or filter by sport/price

alt Matching posts found
    FE --> User: Display filtered post cards and client-side pagination
else No matching posts found
    FE --> User: Display "No se encontraron publicaciones"
end


== View Post Details ==

User -> FE: Click "Ver Detalles" on selected post
FE -> Apache: GET /posts/{id}

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP post details request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display "Post details route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> PostC: Pass authenticated and authorized post details request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden
    FE --> User: Display validation or authorization error
end

PostC -> ORM: Post::with('user')->findOrFail(id)
ORM -> DB: SELECT post with related user WHERE id = ? LIMIT 1

alt Post found
    DB --> ORM: Post and seller record
    ORM --> PostC: Post retrieved

    PostC -> ORM: Review::where(seller_id = post.user.id)->avg('rating')
    ORM -> DB: SELECT AVG(rating) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

    PostC -> ORM: Review::where(seller_id = post.user.id)->count()
    ORM -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM reviews WHERE seller_id = ?

    alt Seller rating lookup success
        DB --> ORM: Seller rating average and review count
        ORM --> PostC: Seller rating metrics retrieved
        PostC --> FE: Return post details JSON
        FE --> User: Display post details modal
    else Seller rating lookup failure
        DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
        ORM --> PostC: Seller rating retrieval failed
        PostC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
        FE --> User: Display system error while loading post details
    end

else Post not found
    DB --> ORM: Empty result set
    ORM --> PostC: Post not found
    PostC --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> User: Display selected post not found error
end


== Remove Post from Profile View ==

User -> FE: Click "Eliminar Publicación" on selected post

alt Delete button available
    FE --> User: Display delete confirmation modal
else Delete action unavailable
    FE --> User: Keep current posts view unchanged
end

User -> FE: Click "Continuar"

FE -> FE: Close delete confirmation modal
FE -> FE: Show delete success toast
FE -> FE: Remove selected post card from profile view
FE -> FE: Update posts tab count
FE -> FE: Reapply client-side post filters and pagination

alt Remaining posts still match filters
    FE --> User: Display updated posts grid
else No remaining posts match filters
    FE --> User: Display "No se encontraron publicaciones"
end

@enduml